{
  "stem": "19895.8",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 142.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bashert ?] is an expression, Yiddish German that it was meant in Heaven.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How can you be so schmaltzy, to talk about a marriage like this?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, what led up to the marriage, it was too, very coincidental.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I am not going to repeat the story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My family, my children, and my wife knows it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We got married 34 years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We dated before we got engaged, we seen each other no longer, no more than four or five weekends.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She lived in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I lived in Washington.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went to New York several times, four or five times.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And by then, I asked if-- I told her I have serious intentions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I would like to marry her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She said she thinks about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then I received a telegram from her, and there was one simple word on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It said igen in Hungarian, which means yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She is Hungarian by birth, but I met her in the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I knew about-- I knew about-- I didn't know her, but I knew her uncle, who was just one year ahead of me in high school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And that's how, when he visited in the United States at the-- at the World Federation of Hungarian Jewish event, I bumped into him and his-- I recognized him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then finally, he recognized me after many years being in the same high school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He talked to me about his visit here from Morocco and that led to my getting to know about this lovely girl, who was love at first sight.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we are married 34 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we have two daughters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My wife's name is Judith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her maiden name is Judith Bardos, B-A-R-D-O-S.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her father and her mother survived the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
